'''Spindel''' is a weaker variant of [[Venenatis]] who is fought in the [[Web Chasm]], a [[singles-plus combat]] area in level 29 [[Wilderness]]. To enter Spindel's lair, players must have completed the [[Wilderness Diary#Hard|hard Wilderness diary]], '''OR''' they must have a Venenatis boss Slayer task (a spider Slayer task does not bypass the diary requirement).

Compared to Venenatis, the fight is easier and safer in return for lower drop quantities and rates.

Killing Spindel counts as a [[Venenatis]] alternative for a slayer Boss task, the [[Wilderness Diary#Elite|elite Wilderness diary]] task, and the combat achievements.

Upon any player entering the chasm, all players inside will be unable to [[teleport]] for {{ticks|3}}. This delay no longer occurs after completion of the [[Wilderness Diary#Hard|hard Wilderness diary]].

